# Tests # 7/DECCARA, 11/DECRARA, and 12/DECSERA will fail unless vttest is
# patched, as DECALN is supposed to reset margins and DECLRMM but vttest does
# not expect this. So fill_screen(void) in vt420.c must be patched to not use
